			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<title>About Us - Renuva</title>
		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			:root {
				--deep-brown: #3e2723;
				--dark-brown: #5c4033;
				--mid-brown: #7a5a3d;
				--brown: #8B6F47;
				--sand: #d4a574;
				--cream: #f6efe8;
				--white: #ffffff;
				--ink: #1e1b18;
			}

			body {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				color: var(--ink);
				background-color: var(--white);
			}

			header {
				background-color: var(--white);
				padding: 1.5rem 0;
				border-bottom: 4px solid var(--sand);
				box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(30, 27, 24, 0.08);
			}

			.header-content {
				max-width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 0 2rem;
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.logo {
				height: 60px;
			}

			.logo img {
				height: 100%;
				width: auto;
			}

			nav a {
				margin-left: 2rem;
				text-decoration: none;
				color: var(--dark-brown);
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-weight: 500;
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
				text-transform: none;
				transition: color 0.3s;
			}

			nav a:hover {
				color: var(--sand);
			}

			.hero {
				position: relative;
				color: var(--white);
				padding: 7rem 2rem;
				text-align: center;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.hero::before {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: url("/assets/images/Screenshot%202026-01-23%20170344.png") center/cover
					no-repeat;
				z-index: 0;
			}

			.hero-content {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				max-width: 900px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
				backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
				padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
				border-radius: 18px;
				color: #1e1b18;
			}

			.hero h1 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-size: 3rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				text-transform: none;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.hero p {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				max-width: 720px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.section {
				max-width: 1200px;
				margin: 4.5rem auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}

			.section-muted {
				background-color: #f3f3f3;
				padding: 4.5rem 0;
				margin: 4.5rem 0;
			}

			.section-muted .section {
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.section-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
				gap: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.section-header h2 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-size: 2.8rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				text-transform: none;
				color: var(--deep-brown);
			}

			.section-header p {
				max-width: 520px;
				color: var(--dark-brown);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}

			.story-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
				gap: 2rem;
				align-items: center;
			}

			.story-text h2 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-size: 3.2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--deep-brown);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				text-transform: none;
			}

			.story-text h3 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				color: var(--deep-brown);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.story-text p {
				margin-bottom: 0;
				line-height: 2.05;
				color: var(--dark-brown);
				font-size: 1.12rem;
			}

			.story-image {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: flex-end;
				padding-left: 6rem;
			}

			.story-image img,
			.feature-image img {
				width: 100%;
				margin-left: auto;
				max-width: 1200px;
				aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
				object-fit: cover;
				border-radius: 16px;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(30, 27, 24, 0.15);
			}

			.feature-row {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
				gap: 2.5rem;
				align-items: center;
				margin-top: 3rem;
			}

			.feature-text h3 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				color: var(--deep-brown);
				margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
			}

			.feature-text p {
				color: var(--dark-brown);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}

			.sustain-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.sustain-card {
				border-radius: 18px;
				overflow: hidden;
				border: 1px solid #eadfd5;
				background-color: var(--white);
				box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(30, 27, 24, 0.08);
			}

			.sustain-card img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 240px;
				object-fit: cover;
			}

			.sustain-card-content {
				padding: 1.5rem;
			}

			.sustain-card-content h3 {
				font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
				color: var(--deep-brown);
			}

			footer {
				background-color: #8b6f47;
				color: var(--white);
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2rem;
				margin-top: 4rem;
			}

			.footer-links {
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}

			.footer-links a {
				color: var(--white);
				text-decoration: none;
				margin: 0 1rem;
				transition: color 0.3s;
			}

			.footer-links a:hover {
				color: var(--white);
			}

			@media (max-width: 860px) {
				.header-content {
					flex-direction: column;
				}

				nav a {
					margin-left: 1rem;
				}

				.hero {
					text-align: center;
				}

				.section-header {
					flex-direction: column;
					align-items: flex-start;
				}
			}

			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				.hero h1 {
					font-size: 2.4rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<div class="header-content">
				<a href="/" style="text-decoration: none;">
					<div class="logo">
						<img src="/assets/images/Renuva.png" alt="Renuva">
					</div>
				</a>
				<nav>
					<a href="/about">About Us</a>
					<a href="/distributor">Distributor</a>
					<a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1>About Us</h1>
				<p>
					Renuva wraps give kitchens a premium new look without the downtime of a full remodel.
					We combine craftsmanship, durable materials, and clean installation so homeowners can
					refresh their space fast.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="story-grid">
				<div class="story-text">
					<h2>"Our Story"</h2>
					<p>
						Renuva makes premium kitchen transformations attainable, bringing refined finishes
						and durable wraps to everyday homes without the time or cost of full remodels. We
						focus on clean lines, careful detailing, and materials that feel elevated the moment
						you walk in, so your space looks custom without the long construction timeline. Our
						team works quickly, keeps disruption low, and delivers a finished look that feels
						bespoke and built to last.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<img
						src="/assets/images/Wrapping%20mats.png"
						alt="Wrapping mats used for surface transformations"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section-muted">
			<div class="section">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Sustainability at the core</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="sustain-grid">
				<div class="sustain-card">
					<img src="/assets/images/Beigetheme.png" alt="Beige themed wrap finish" />
					<div class="sustain-card-content">
						<h3>Eco-minded materials</h3>
						<p>Designed to minimize waste and extend the life of existing surfaces.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sustain-card">
					<img src="/assets/images/Browntheme.png" alt="Brown themed wrap finish" />
					<div class="sustain-card-content">
						<h3>Home-friendly installation</h3>
						<p>Clean, quiet installs that fit around your daily routine.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sustain-card">
					<img src="/assets/images/Greytheme.png" alt="Grey themed wrap finish" />
					<div class="sustain-card-content">
						<h3>Built for longevity</h3>
						<p>Durable finishes that keep homes looking fresh for years.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<p>&copy; 2026 Renuva Kitchen Wrapping. All rights reserved.</p>
			<p>Transform your kitchen, renew your space.</p>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
				<a href="/about">About</a>
				<a href="/">Home</a>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
